      "updated": 1783463317962,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Functional Requirement\n1. User should be able to see some\nrecommendation on shops/restaurants\nbased on their preferences and flight\ntimings on their mobile app/desktop app\n2. Recommendations are sent to users via\npush notification to their phone",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "V_5QIQHo1ZW-VamSG6g6q",
      "originalText": "Functional Requirement\n1. User should be able to see some recommendation on shops/restaurants based on their preferences and flight timings on their mobile app/desktop app\n2. Recommendations are sent to users via push notification to their phone",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
