      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1783467602592,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Non-functional Requirement\n1. Availability>> Consistency (any\nrestaurant/shop not listed in\nrecommendations immediately should not\nbe a deal breaker)\n2. Low latency <= 500ms\n3. Scalable: 100s of airpots * 100s of\noutlets * 1000s of travellers ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "O0NuOGMuApWnANvOKhqPz",
      "originalText": "Non-functional Requirement\n1. Availability>> Consistency (any restaurant/shop not listed in recommendations immediately should not be a deal breaker)\n2. Low latency <= 500ms\n3. Scalable: 100s of airpots * 100s of outlets * 1000s of travellers ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
