      "text": "Flow:\nThe recommendation service is triggered in three ways:\n1. Hourly scheduler: This triggers every hour and the\nrecommendation service will fetch all the users who have a\nflight booking in the next 6hrs and pushed recommendations\nto their phone\n2. get-recommendations API: This API is triggered when a\nuser logs in to their mobile app or website. This time\nrecommendation service will take user preferences and shows\nrecommendation within the app\n3. Live feed of any sales: The recommendation service\nsubscribes to the live feed system which contains messages\nwith ongoing sales at any airport. The recommendation engine\nwill consume this feed, check which all users have the sale\nstore in their recommendation list from the cache, overwrite\nthe new recommendation and pushes the sale details directly\nto their phone.\n ",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "-B7gU4xgbZqcPDAx8GxCK",
      "originalText": "Flow:\nThe recommendation service is triggered in three ways:\n1. Hourly scheduler: This triggers every hour and the recommendation service will fetch all the users who have a flight booking in the next 6hrs and pushed recommendations to their phone\n2. get-recommendations API: This API is triggered when a user logs in to their mobile app or website. This time recommendation service will take user preferences and shows recommendation within the app\n3. Live feed of any sales: The recommendation service subscribes to the live feed system which contains messages with ongoing sales at any airport. The recommendation engine will consume this feed, check which all users have the sale store in their recommendation list from the cache, overwrite the new recommendation and pushes the sale details directly to their phone.\n ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
